{"word":"πρόβατον","slug":"πρόβατον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πρόβατον, ου, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:προβαίνω\">προβαίνω</a></el>] <b>a sheep<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of an animal in the care of a shepherd <b><a href='B:470 7:15'>Mt 7:15</a>; <a href='B:480 6:34'>Mk 6:34</a>; <a href='B:490 15:4'>Lk 15:4</a>, <a href='B:490 15:6'>6</a>; <a href='B:500 2:14'>J 2:14f</a>; <a href='B:510 8:32'>Ac 8:32</a>; <a href='B:520 8:36'>Ro 8:36</a>; <a href='B:670 2:25'>1 Pt 2:25</a></b> (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὡς\">ὡς</a></el> introduces ordinary sheep as a model for understanding humans who go astray); <b><a href='B:730 18:13'>Rv 18:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> in care of a leader/shepherd <b><a href='B:470 10:6'>Mt 10:6</a>; <a href='B:470 15:24'>15:24</a>; <a href='B:470 25:32'>25:32f</a>; <a href='B:500 10:7'>J 10:7</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in J; <b><a href='B:650 13:20'>Hb 13:20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:προβάτιον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:προβεβηκώς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}